<HEAD>Posh Suburb Shaken by Violence; It Can Happen Here</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 4th graf pvs: `School District... to UPDATE suspect
found dead; SUBS 11th and 12th graf, pvs: `Reporters were... with
